### Safety / UX Constraints

- The supervisor must **only** manage an allowlisted set of daemon specs (no arbitrary command execution from user input).
- Daemon logs must be redacted for secrets; log streaming should be bounded.
- UI must clearly distinguish “Gateway is running” vs “Gateway is ready (dependencies healthy)”.

