│  ├── Display fleet status in web UI                                         │
│  ├── Route agent-sweep plans through approval workflow (SLB integration)    │
│  └── Archive agent-sweep results to CASS for learning                       │
│                                                                             │
└─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

